                put on and turn on your PICO, the "Karga" game will be displayed in the available apps.</strong></p><a
                href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7Kp8zoLv0Fw&t=50s" style="color: #8b2062;">TIME CODE</a>
        </li>
