                    href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7Kp8zoLv0Fw&t=67s" style="color: #8b2062;">TIME
                CODE</a></strong></p>
        </li>
        <li style="color: #8b2062;">
            <p style="color: #8b2062;"><strong>Click to install <a
                    href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?t=71&v=7Kp8zoLv0Fw&feature=youtu.be" style="color: #8b2062;">TIME
